Package com.ibm.itim.dataservices.model.pim

Extends the com.ibm.itim.dataservices.model package to provide a remotable application programming interface for Shared Access Module objects.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CredentialComponent Interface for a credential or credential pool object.
 

Class Summary
Credential This is a value Object class that holds the attribute information of a credential in the data model.
CredentialLease This value Object class holds the attribute information of a credential lease in the data model.
CredentialPool This value Object class holds the attribute information of a credential pool in the data model.
CredentialSetting This class holds the credential settings for a credential object in the data model.
GlobalCredentialSetting This class holds the global credential settings
SAEntitlement This class represents an entitlement of the shared access policy.
SAEntitlementCredentialObject This class represents an shared access policy entitlement with a specific credential or crdential pool.
SAEntitlementCriteria This class represents a shared access policy entitlement with a set of criteria.
SAMembership This class represents the people memberships of the policy.
SharedAccessPolicy Value Object class that holds the attribute information of a shared access policy in the data model.
 

Enum Summary
Credential.AccessMode Enumeration constants of credential access mode
Credential.Status Enumeration constants of credential status
CredentialLease.STATUS Enumeration of status
GlobalCredentialSetting.LEASE_EXPIRATION_NOTIFICATION_MODE The valid values for lease expiration handling.
NOTIFY_ONLY indicates upon expiration, notification email will be sent.
NOTIFY_AND_CHECKIN indicates upon expiration, credential will be automatically checked-in and lesse will be notified
SAEntitlement.DefinitionType Enumeration of entitlement definition type
SAEntitlement.Type Enumeration of entitlement type
SAMembership.Type Membership type values
 

Package com.ibm.itim.dataservices.model.pim Description

Extends the com.ibm.itim.dataservices.model package to provide a remotable application programming interface for Shared Access Module objects.

For a high-level overview, see the Data Services API Overview
